title: Trees: Oak Forest - Vol. 1 (Extreme Realistic Wind)
description: A big variety of realistic oak trees with dynamic wind system
longDescription:
September 24, 2024:

This high-quality asset contains 100 tree meshes with realistic wind animations, 15 small plants, 6 photo scanned trunks, some branches and some grass. Choose between summer, autumn and leafless tree variant. Moreover, you have various options to configure the wind strength and the wind animation speed (light / strong breeze, mixed wind and random wind). Some maps already contain a few different camera perspectives. The most beautiful scenes were selected for this.

The bark texture can be replaced with a custom texture for each tree! You can choose between four different leaf types and change them very easily. An outstanding advantage of this asset is its uniqueness: Not only are the 8K/4K leaves of all the trees interchangeable, you are capable of dynamically configuring the colour of them as well.

The bent trees have exclusively 'light breeze' wind!

All maps use the new 'SunSky' Blueprint with different lighting scenes.

With the help of procedural foliage spawner types you can create big forests in seconds!


Current Minimum Specs:

  • 12-Cores CPU @ 3.4 GHz
  • 32 GB RAM
  • Nvidia RTX 3070 Ti
  • At least 10GB of VRAM


Required disk space: 7GB


Please note:

If you buy the 'Big Forest Pack' you will not only save money (contains Trees Vol. 1-5), you will also get 11 additional forest maps (5 different variations of the 66 km² map) with different lighting scenes, seasons and a lot of extra content.


For further questions please come to our Discord!
technicalDetails:
Requirements:

  • This product supports Nanite and Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.2+
  • Product uses VSM and Hardware Ray Tracing by default.
  • Product uses 'SunPosition' plugin and 'Volumetrics' by default.


Features:

  • realistic wind animated trees
  • 1 parameter to change the wind strength / wind animation speed
  • ﻿4 square kilometre map
  • 10 example maps
  • change leafs density
  • procedural foliage spawner
  • customizable master materials
  • different exposure settings
  • interchangeable trunk section above roots with moss bark
  • [5] seamless forest ground texture sets
  • [6] different high-quality leaf albedo textures
  • [21] trees [6] trunks [16] plants [10] meadow

Texture Sizes:

  •  [5] Texture sets in (4096x4096 to 2048x2048) ground
  •  [6] Texture sets in (8192x8192 to 4096x4096) tree leaves
  •  [2] Texture set in (2048x2048) bark


Collision: Yes, Custom and Generated

Vertex Count:

bushes: 7k-190

small trees: 18k

high vert trees: 125k-55k

low vert trees: 51k-33k

LODs: None (Nanite fallback)

Number of Meshes: 324

Number of Materials: 65 Master Materials, 4000 Material Instances

Number of Textures: 676

Platforms Tested: PC
